  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency WASH and Livelihoods Response for IDPs in Kohat District.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is in response to ongoing fighting between militants and security forces in Orakzai Agency , Pakistan which has resulted in a large displacement of civilians out of the affected areas/.  The project aims to relieve suffering, maintain health and reduce vulnerability by:&#xB7;   1. Providing water and sanitation and hygiene supplies  2. Promoting public health and hygiene practices  3. Building capacity of local organizations and line agencies to respond better to WASH emergencies       in the future.</narrative>
  </description>
